{"tid":2111240,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己越黎越淫","createTime":"2020-07-16T11:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T13:16:06.000Z","uid":33709,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b0b6cc07b7c9085bd41f8f8348c215083a330f","tid":2111240,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"覺得自己越嚟越淫<br />\n仔仔自從操咗尖，d肌肉結實咗又望落好J咗，成日想比佢入。（以前佢肥肉多但唔係去到豬個類）<br />\n<br />\n以前會間中輪流上大家屋企睇下Netflix, 玩下其他野咁。依家上屋企，好想拉佢沖涼洗乾淨幫佢口再比佢入....好想比佢入我...佢都問我做咩依排主動咗，我扮傻話可能太耐無打，餓嘛～所以咪想要<br />\n<br />\n我地本身唔係個啲成日做既情侶，本身一個月先一次左右，個陣佢肥覺得鐘意佢對我好但唔夠feel引起性慾，真係餓先想搞...依家佢操到有左肌肉線條，搞到一星期搞一次咁濟，總知一有時間就想同佢搞，我對住仔仔真係變到越嚟越淫。"},{"pid":"9f445e16fe4025cccf520d5e27c155c0b092e509","tid":2111240,"uid":60434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:56:43.000Z","msg":"好gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ba19630177d43b33e650b6c24b1bca3a218187","tid":2111240,"uid":295672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af8488b1118570d76cc72c8a78bf61307160e1dc","tid":2111240,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27005ed68c35e7a833947b3b8e40142b55e6df87","tid":2111240,"uid":213560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"Gay post"},{"pid":"56d9b42a404997f2d64ebde8b7673a69d8cd0c97","tid":2111240,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:58:19.000Z","msg":"玩少啲屎忽，小心肛裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbf78aec7f2ac00bb88019c59eb2c6b5669d620","tid":2111240,"uid":75196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"